Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:13.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:17.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see what I want tonight
